videos.description: Iowa State's Marial Shayok gets Lagerald Vick in the air on a pump fake and cans the step-back 3 in the first half.
videos.headline: Shayok buries nasty step-back 3

videos.description: Tyrese Haliburton drives to the paint and whips a no-look pass to Cameron Lard for the two-handed flush for Iowa State.
videos.headline: Lard slams off of Haliburton's no-look dime

videos.description: Marial Shayok buries a wide-open 3 to stay a perfect 5-for-5 from downtown to balloon Iowa State's lead to 16.
videos.headline: Shayok splashes 5th straight 3 on Kansas breakdown

videos.description: Iowa State continues to pour it on Kansas as Tyrese Haliburton tees up a 3 from NBA range and connects.
videos.headline: Haliburton drains 3 from way downtown
